data.description: Welcome to this fantastic ranch-style home offering 3 bedrooms, 2 baths, and an unbeatable opportunity for both living and investing! Step inside to discover a space that proudly showcases beautiful hardwood floors throughout. The kitchen is a chef's dream, featuring 42-inch shaker cabinets with under cabinet lighting, a sleek stainless hood vent, stainless steel appliances, and a modern gray and white color scheme. The spacious bedrooms provide comfort and relaxation, while the huge unfinished basement holds endless potential for customization and expansion to suit your needs. Outside, a great deck awaits for entertaining and enjoying outdoor gatherings with family and friends. Conveniently located near Frederick Douglass High School, the Georgia Dome, Downtown Atlanta, and major thoroughfares including I-285 and I-20, this home offers easy access to everything the vibrant city has to offer. Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity to make this your own! Schedule your viewing today.
